T02TD2848E:185b-1: sa ha sra bh'u dza nee tra s'a dha nam /
T02TD2848E:185b-3: phyag stong spyan stong gi sgrub thangs [?]/
T02TD2848E:185b-4: 'phags pa phyag na rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2848E:185b-5: 'jig rten rnams kyi mgon po mchog / dkar po thugs rje rtags 'chang ba'i //
T02TD2848E:185b-7: dam pa de la phyag 'tshal nas //
T02TD2848E:185b-8: bdag nyid dran phyir sgrub thabs gang //
T02TD2848E:185b-9: nges pa'i shes pas bri bar bya //
T02TD2848E:185b-10: 'gro ba rnams kyis dben pa yi //
T02TD2848E:185b-11: yid du 'ong ba'i sa phyogs su //
T02TD2848E:185b-12: sa gzhi legs par byugs byas la //
T02TD2848E:185b-13: me tog dri zhim bkram byas te //
T02TD2848E:185b-14: gcig dang sbyar bas 'dug pa'i stan //
T02TD2848E:185b-15: bde ba la 'dug byas nas ni //
T02TD2848E:185b-16: 'gro ba'i don du sems bskyed la //
T02TD2848E:185b-17: snying gar ram las gyur pa yi //
T02TD2848E:185b-19: de steng thugs yid las gyur pa'i //
T02TD2848E:185b-20: gnod mdzes rgyal por bdag bsams te //
T02TD2848E:185b-21: chu shing ram shing sbyar ba'i sgras //
T02TD2848E:185b-22: phyogs bcu dag tu sdigs mdzub dang //
T02TD2848E:185b-23: sngags kyis yang dag bskrad par bya //
T02TD2848E:185b-24: aom sarba bi ghn'ana ha na ha na h'um phat raksha raksha sv'a h'a /
T02TD2848E:185b-25: de nas bdag nyid snying ga las //
T02TD2848E:185b-26: aa las ri bong can bsam nas //
T02TD2848E:185b-27: de ni thugs mchog bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD2848E:185b-28: de las 'od zer nag po dag / sa gzhi dag la spros byas pas //
T02TD2848E:185b-29: sa gzhi la sogs rdo rjer gyur //
T02TD2848E:185b-31: gur dang bla re dra ba dang //
T02TD2848E:185b-32: shin tu mngon par bsgom par bya //
T02TD2848E:185b-33: de nas nam mkha' bla ma dang //
T02TD2848E:185b-34: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' dag / sngon du mngon sum dmigs pa la //
T02TD2848E:185b-35: phyag 'tshal ba dang mchod pa dang //
T02TD2848E:185b-36: sdig pa bshags dang yi rang dang //
T02TD2848E:186a-2: sems bskyed pa dang gnas bzhi dang //
T02TD2848E:186a-3: mthar ni stong nyid bsgom pa'o //
T02TD2848E:186a-4: don gyis dngos por bsams nas ni //
T02TD2848E:186a-5: sngags 'di myur du bklag par bya //
T02TD2848E:186a-6: aom sva bh'a ba shuddha:sarba dharm'a:sva bh'a ba shuddhonya\ham /
T02TD2848E:186a-7: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bh'a ba a'atma konya\ham /
T02TD2848E:186a-8: de dag nang du bsam bya ba //
T02TD2848E:186a-9: ya wa ra la rnam bzhi pa //
T02TD2848E:186a-10: steng du sna ldan gzhag pa las //
T02TD2848E:186a-11: dbang chen chu bdag 'bar ba dang //
T02TD2848E:186a-12: skyed par byed pa rnam bzhi yi //
T02TD2848E:186a-13: dkyil 'khor kha dog rnam bzhi rnams //
T02TD2848E:186a-14: rim pa bzhin du rnam par bsgom //
T02TD2848E:186a-15: de steng sum las ri rab ni //
T02TD2848E:186a-16: rin chen sna bzhis yang dag gnas //
T02TD2848E:186a-17: de dag yongs su gyur pa las //
T02TD2848E:186a-18: khang pa brtsegs pa bsam bya ba //
T02TD2848E:186a-19: gru bzhi pa la sgo bzhi pa //
T02TD2848E:186a-20: ka pa brgyad kyis nye bar brgyan //
T02TD2848E:186a-21: ye shes sna lnga'i rtsig pa dag / phyogs bzhi dag tu brgyan nas kyang //
T02TD2848E:186a-22: dra ba dra phyed dag dang ni //
T02TD2848E:186a-23: rin chen pha bu dag dang ni //
T02TD2848E:186a-24: gru bzhi par ni brgyan pa yin //
T02TD2848E:186a-25: tva ra na ni bzhis brgyan cing //
T02TD2848E:186a-26: mdzes pa'i padma'i phreng ba dang //
T02TD2848E:186a-28: grva bzhi dag tu dpag bsam shing //
T02TD2848E:186a-29: chen po bzhi dang klu rgyal dang //
T02TD2848E:186a-30: sprin dang phyogs skyong zhing srung rnams //
T02TD2848E:186a-31: yang dag par ni dgod par bya //
T02TD2848E:186a-32: de dkyil thig ni bzhi btab pas //
T02TD2848E:186a-33: dkyil 'khor dgu ru gyur pa la //
T02TD2848E:186a-34: dkyil du bcom ldan phyag stong pa //
T02TD2848E:186a-35: kha dog dkar po ldem bag can //
T02TD2848E:186a-36: zhal gdong bcu gcig phyag bco brgyad //
T02TD2848E:186a-37: dbu ma'i zhal gsum dkar la mdzes //
T02TD2848E:186a-38: lhag ma khre zhal 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
T02TD2848E:186a-39: kun gyi steng na 'od dpag med //
T02TD2848E:186a-40: padma'i rigs kyi phyag rgyas btab //
T02TD2848E:186a-41: dang po phyag gnyis snying ga na //
T02TD2848E:186a-42: thal mo nges par sbyar ba yin //
T02TD2848E:186a-43: de 'og g-yas na dgra sta dang //
T02TD2848E:186a-44: de 'og gri gug rnon po yin //
T02TD2848E:186a-45: padma ral gri zhags pa dang //
T02TD2848E:186a-46: ljon shing me long bsil yab dag / rim pa bzhin du gnas pa yin //
T02TD2848E:186a-47: g-yon pa'i phyag ni de 'og dag / rdo rje dril bu mnga' gzhu dang //
T02TD2848E:186a-48: lcags kyi bum pa 'khor lo dang //
T02TD2848E:186a-49: gdugs dang rin chen 'bar ba rnams //
T02TD2848E:186a-50: rim pa bzhin du bsnams par mdzad //
T02TD2848E:186a-51: rdo rje bsnams pa'i phyag gis ni //
T02TD2848E:186a-52: lha mo padma'i sgrol ma la //
T02TD2848E:186a-53: gnyis su med pas 'khyud par mdzad //
T02TD2848E:186b-0: lha mo @186b de ni zhal gcig ste //
T02TD2848E:186b-1: phyag ni drug tu nges pa ste //
T02TD2848E:186b-2: dang po'i g-yas pas autpal gyi //
T02TD2848E:186b-3: steng na padma brgyad bsnams pas //
T02TD2848E:186b-4: thugs rje che ba 'khyud par mdzad //
T02TD2848E:186b-6: g-yon pa'i dang pos me long dang ;
T02TD2848E:186b-7: / bsil yab bum pa bsnams par mdzad //
T02TD2848E:186b-8: h'um dang pam las gyur pa yi //
T02TD2848E:186b-9: phyag stong yum bcas de ltar bsgom //
T02TD2848E:186b-10: de yi shar gyi dkyil 'khor la //
T02TD2848E:186b-11: yi ge bam las gyur pa yi //
T02TD2848E:186b-12: rdo rje padma zhes bya ba / gzhal gcig kha dog dkar po can //
T02TD2848E:186b-13: phyag g-yas dang po autpal gyi //
T02TD2848E:186b-15: de steng rdo rje rtse dgu pa //
T02TD2848E:186b-16: sngon po nyid kyis bsnams par mdzad //
T02TD2848E:186b-18: g-yon gyi dang pos dril bu 'dzin //
T02TD2848E:186b-19: de 'og lcags kyi dgra sta dag / phyar ba nyid kyis bsnams par mdzad //
T02TD2848E:186b-20: lho phyogs dkyil 'khor sngon po la //
T02TD2848E:186b-21: yi ge ram las gyur pa yi //
T02TD2848E:186b-22: rin chen padma bsam bya ba //
T02TD2848E:186b-23: g-yas kyi dang po autpal gyi //
T02TD2848E:186b-25: de steng rin chen zur brgyad pa //
T02TD2848E:186b-27: lhag ma shar gyi bcom ldan ltar //
T02TD2848E:186b-28: phyag mtshan rnams ni bsnams par mdzad //
T02TD2848E:186b-29: nub kyi dkyil 'khor dmar po la //
T02TD2848E:186b-30: mum yig 'bar ba las gyur pa'i //
T02TD2848E:186b-31: thub pa'i padma bsgom bya ba //
T02TD2848E:186b-32: g-yas kyi dang po rang nyid kyi //
T02TD2848E:186b-33: mtshan ma rnams ni bsnams par mdzad //
T02TD2848E:186b-34: lhag ma shar gyi bcom ldan ltar //
T02TD2848E:186b-35: phyag mtshan rnams ni bsnams par mdzad //
T02TD2848E:186b-36: byang gi dkyil 'khor ljang gu la //
T02TD2848E:186b-37: bcom ldan las kyi padma ni //
T02TD2848E:186b-38: yi ge kam las gyur pa ste //
T02TD2848E:186b-39: g-yas kyi dang por rang nyid rtags //
T02TD2848E:186b-40: phyag gzhan gong ma rnams bzhin no //
T02TD2848E:186b-41: shar lhor rdo rje sgrol ma ni //
T02TD2848E:186b-42: lha mo sku mdog sngo skya la //
T02TD2848E:186b-43: zhal gcig phyag ni drug pa'i dbyibs //
T02TD2848E:186b-44: g-yas kyi dang po autpal te //
T02TD2848E:186b-45: chu skyes 'dab ma brgyad pa la //
T02TD2848E:186b-46: rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams par mdzad //
T02TD2848E:186b-47: phyag gzhan gri gug padma dang //
T02TD2848E:186b-48: me long bsil yab bum pa bsnams //
T02TD2848E:186b-49: ba yig las gyur de ltar bsam //
T02TD2848E:186b-50: lho nub rin chen sgrol ma ni //
T02TD2848E:186b-51: ram yig las gyur dmar ser mdog / phyag g-yas dang po rang nyid rtags //
T02TD2848E:186b-52: lha mo rdo rje sgrol ma bzhin //
T02TD2848E:186b-53: nub byang thub pa'i sgrol ma ni //
T02TD2848E:186b-54: mum yig las gyur ljang dmar mdog /
T02TD2848E:187a-0: @187a * // dang po rang gi rtags 'chang pa'o //
T02TD2848E:187a-1: byang shar las kyi sgrol ma ni //
T02TD2848E:187a-2: gam yig las gyur ljang skya'i mdog / phyag g-yas rang gi rtags 'chang zhing //
T02TD2848E:187a-3: phyag gzhan gong ma rnams dang mtshungs //
T02TD2848E:187a-4: grva bzhir rin chen bum pa bzhi //
T02TD2848E:187a-5: kha dog rnam bzhis rnam par gnas //
T02TD2848E:187a-6: de yi phyi rol snam bu la //
T02TD2848E:187a-7: ling tshe bcu drug bri bya ste //
T02TD2848E:187a-8: phyag na rdo rje 'jam dbyangs dang //
T02TD2848E:187a-9: kun gzigs sgrib pa rnam sel dag / zhal gcig phyag ni gnyis pa la //
T02TD2848E:187a-10: kha dog rnam bzhis rnam par gnas //
T02TD2848E:187a-11: g-yas na rdo rje autpal dang //
T02TD2848E:187a-12: padma sna tshogs rdo rje bsnams //
T02TD2848E:187a-13: 'gying bag tshul du gnas par mdzad //
T02TD2848E:187a-14: g-yon pa dang ba'i phyag rgya'o //
T02TD2848E:187a-15: de dag kun gyi g-yon rol du //
T02TD2848E:187a-16: sgeg mo rin chen phreng ba dang //
T02TD2848E:187a-17: dbyangs dang gar gyis mnyes mdzad rnams //
T02TD2848E:187a-18: rang rang phyag rgyas yang dag gnas //
T02TD2848E:187a-19: byams pa nam mkha'i snying po dang //
T02TD2848E:187a-20: kun bzangs yi snying po dag / rang rang kha dog phyag rgya yis //
T02TD2848E:187a-21: de yi cha la rnam par gnas //
T02TD2848E:187a-22: de g-yon me tog bdug spos dang //
T02TD2848E:187a-23: mar me dri chab lha mo rnams //
T02TD2848E:187a-24: rang nyid kha dog phyag mtshan gyis //
T02TD2848E:187a-25: yang dag par ni gnas pa'o //
T02TD2848E:187a-26: lha rnams de dag thams cad ni //
T02TD2848E:187a-27: phyag rgya lnga yis rnam par brgyan //
T02TD2848E:187a-28: padma'i steng na nyi zla yi //
T02TD2848E:187a-29: steng na rab tu gnas pa'o //
T02TD2848E:187a-30: shar dang lho dang nub dang byang //
T02TD2848E:187a-31: sgo rnams na ni sgo skyong dag / shes rab mthar byed gshin mthar byed //
T02TD2848E:187a-32: padma mthar byed bgegs mthar rnams //
T02TD2848E:187a-33: dbu gsum phyag ni drug pa la //
T02TD2848E:187a-34: 'jigs pa'i gzugs kyi cha lugs can //
T02TD2848E:187a-35: phyag g-yas dang po ral gri dang //
T02TD2848E:187a-37: lhag ma lcags kyu zhags pa dang //
T02TD2848E:187a-38: rtse gsum lcags sgrog dam pa'i bdag / rdo rje brag gi steng gnas pa'o //
T02TD2848E:187a-39: de nas dam tshig sems dpa' yi //
T02TD2848E:187a-40: thugs las 'od zer spros nas kyang //
T02TD2848E:187a-41: ye shes 'khor lo spyan drangs nas //
T02TD2848E:187a-42: mdun du yang dag mchod par bya //
T02TD2848E:187a-43: sngags dang phyag rgyas sbyor shes pas //
T02TD2848E:187a-44: dam tshig 'khor lo myur du gzhug / de nas rang gi sa bon las //
T02TD2848E:187a-45: 'od zer nam mkha'i phyogs spros nas //
T02TD2848E:187a-46: padma'i sgrol sogs lha mo lngas //
T02TD2848E:187a-47: ye shes lnga yi bum pa yis //
T02TD2848E:187a-48: chu yis bdag la dbang bskur ba'o //
T02TD2848E:187a-49: aom aa bhi shinytsa tu m'am lo ka n'a th'a ya h'um /
T02TD2848E:187a-50: de nas bdag nyid snying ga la //
T02TD2848E:187b-0: ri bong can @187b dang shing rta bcu //
T02TD2848E:187b-1: kha sbyor phur mar gnas pa yi //
T02TD2848E:187b-2: nang du chu skyes 'dab ma brgyad //
T02TD2848E:187b-3: de steng dug gsum yi ge ni //
T02TD2848E:187b-4: kha dog dkar po rnam par gnas //
T02TD2848E:187b-5: de la bstod nas dkar po ni //
T02TD2848E:187b-6: rgyan rnams kun gyis brgyan pa'o //
T02TD2848E:187b-7: 'phrog dang nang dang kun gyi steng //
T02TD2848E:187b-8: dug gsum yi ges rnam par brgyan //
T02TD2848E:187b-10: phyogs bcu dag tu spros pa las //
T02TD2848E:187b-11: 'gro ba sems can thams cad ni //
T02TD2848E:187b-12: nyon mongs thams cad sbyangs byas nas //
T02TD2848E:187b-14: de dag rim par bsdus pa las //
T02TD2848E:187b-15: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje can //
T02TD2848E:187b-16: lha yi sku ni bsgom par bya //
T02TD2848E:187b-17: de ni rang bzhin 'od gsal ba'o //
T02TD2848E:187b-18: bsgoms pas skyon sngags bzlas pa //
T02TD2848E:187b-19: mu tig phreng ba'i tshul gyis su //
T02TD2848E:187b-20: steng nas steng du 'bar ba ni //
T02TD2848E:187b-21: rang bzhin 'khor bar rnam par bsam //
T02TD2848E:187b-22: dang po dag dang bar gnas pa'i //
T02TD2848E:187b-23: tha ma dag gis bsdus pa yi //
T02TD2848E:187b-24: sngags kyis yang dag bzlas par bya //
T02TD2848E:187b-26: sa ha sra badzra bhu dzanee tra /
T02TD2848E:187b-27: n'i la kantha lo ke shva r'a ya h'um h'um phat /
T02TD2848E:187b-34: aom mu ni t'a re h'um /
T02TD2848E:187b-39: aom sa manta ka ka h'um /
T02TD2848E:187b-40: aom ni bar na bi skambhi h'um /
T02TD2848E:187b-46: aom aa gang sam gu ra be h'um /
T02TD2848E:187b-47: aom sa manta bha dre h'um /
T02TD2848E:187b-51: aom padma a'a lo ke h'um /
T02TD2848E:187b-53: aom pra dzny'a nta ka h'um /
T02TD2848E:187b-57: mchod pa dag ni nyi shu yi //
T02TD2848E:187b-58: sngags dang phyag rgyas yang dag mchod //
T02TD2848E:187b-59: yi ge brgya pa'i gsang sngags ni //
T02TD2848E:187b-60: rtag tu 'don pa nyid du bya //
T02TD2848E:187b-61: lam du zhugs dang 'chags pa'i tshe //
T02TD2848E:187b-62: spyod lam la ni spros pa na //
T02TD2848E:187b-63: rdo rje rtse gcig phyag rgyas ni //
T02TD2848E:187b-64: 'od byung steng la snying po yi //
T02TD2848E:187b-65: sngags de yongs su gyur pa dang //
T02TD2848E:187b-66: cho ga gsum las rtogs pa yi //
T02TD2848E:187b-67: rim pa bzhin du lha bsams nas //
T02TD2848E:187b-68: yan lag bzhi la rab tu bstim //
T02TD2848E:187b-69: cho ga'i phyag rgya dpa' bo lnga //
T02TD2848E:187b-70: phyag rgya 'di yis lus mdzes pa'o //
T02TD2848E:188a-2: bdag nyid phrin las rnam bzhi yi //
T02TD2848E:188a-3: rnal 'byor yang dag bsam byas la //
T02TD2848E:188a-4: las kyi dang po zhi ba mchod //
T02TD2848E:188a-5: dkyil 'khor khru gang zlum po la //
T02TD2848E:188a-6: padma'i phreng bas nang bskor zhing //
T02TD2848E:188a-7: rdo rje 'bar ba'i phreng ba dag / de yi phyi rim bri byas la //
T02TD2848E:188a-8: dri zhim dkar po zhor ldan pa'i //
T02TD2848E:188a-9: bsreg cing ku shas bcings te gzugs //
T02TD2848E:188a-10: gu gul me tog ku sha dang //
T02TD2848E:188a-11: mar dang 'bras thug til dang ni //
T02TD2848E:188a-12: 'o thug lung thang sngon po dag / las kyi sngags ni mthar sbyar la //
T02TD2848E:188a-13: me lha de yi snying ga yi //
T02TD2848E:188a-14: mkha' la 'khor lo bsam byas te //
T02TD2848E:188a-15: bdag nyid dam tshig sems dpa' yi //
T02TD2848E:188a-16: rim pa bzhin du mchod pa'o //
T02TD2848E:188a-17: bya ba rnams ni thams cad la //
T02TD2848E:188a-18: de yi ngo bos mnyam par gzhag / de nas bstod pa bya ba ni //
T02TD2848E:188a-19: sangs rgyas kun gyi gzugs kyi sku //
T02TD2848E:188a-20: chos kyi sku ste gzhan gyi mchog / sngags kyi mgon po mchog gi lha //
T02TD2848E:188a-21: snying rje'i bdag nyid phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD2848E:188a-22: ye shes rdo rje stobs po che //
T02TD2848E:188a-23: shin tu nges pas zhi ba'i tshul //
T02TD2848E:188a-24: theg pa chen po'i go 'phang thob //
T02TD2848E:188a-25: rdo rje chos la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD2848E:188a-26: shin tu dag pa'i dpa' bo che //
T02TD2848E:188a-27: mchog gi dbang phyug kun gyi mgon //
T02TD2848E:188a-28: dam chos mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i //
T02TD2848E:188a-30: cir yang mi dmigs stong pa'i dang //
T02TD2848E:188a-31: lhan cig skyes pa'i ral gri bsnams //
T02TD2848E:188a-32: mi rtog ye shes go cha can //
T02TD2848E:188a-34: de nas zas kyi rnal 'byor ni //
T02TD2848E:188a-35: chu yi dkyil 'khor de la yang //
T02TD2848E:188a-36: ram las me yi dkyil 'khor ni //
T02TD2848E:188a-37: gru gsum 'bar ba bsam byas nas //
T02TD2848E:188a-38: de dkyil tshogs kyi 'khor lo yang //
T02TD2848E:188a-39: gsal bar rab tu bsam byas nas //
T02TD2848E:188a-40: snod ni rab las rin chen ni //
T02TD2848E:188a-41: rang bzhin 'bar bar bsgom byas nas //
T02TD2848E:188a-42: der ni kha zas sna tshogs rnams //
T02TD2848E:188a-43: bsams nas de dkyil rdo rje ni //
T02TD2848E:188a-44: rtsa lnga rab tu 'bar ba las //
T02TD2848E:188a-45: bdud rtsir gyur par rab tu bsam //
T02TD2848E:188a-46: de nas rang gi sa bon las //
T02TD2848E:188a-47: 'od zer kha dog sna lnga dag / nam mkha'i phyogs su 'phros pa las //
T02TD2848E:188a-48: phyogs dus kun na bzhugs pa yi //
T02TD2848E:188a-49: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
T02TD2848E:188a-50: mdzod spur zhugs nas thugs kyi ni //
T02TD2848E:188b-0: bdud rtsi blangs @188b nas de nyid du //
T02TD2848E:188b-2: byin gyis brlabs nas bza' bar bya //
T02TD2848E:188b-4: bdag gi 'jig rten mgon po yi //
T02TD2848E:188b-5: sgrub pa'i thabs 'di byas pa yis //
T02TD2848E:188b-6: sems can 'gro ba mtha' dag la //
T02TD2848E:188b-7: nyon mongs sgrab pa kun bsal nas //
T02TD2848E:188b-8: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje can //
T02TD2848E:188b-9: lha yi sku ni thob par shog / slob dpon chen po dngos grub brnyes pa /
T02TD2848E:188b-10: ta th'a ga ta badzra'i zhal snga nas mdzad pa /
T02TD2848E:188b-11: bcom ldan 'das phyag stong spyan stong gi sgrub thabs rdzogs so /
T02TD2848E:188b-13: // / mkhas pa'i 'byung gnas shar phyogs bham ga la'i //
T02TD2848E:188b-14: nyi ma 'byung gnas zla ba zhes bya ba //
T02TD2848E:188b-15: mkhas pa chen po de yi zhal snga nas //
T02TD2848E:188b-16: bod kyi lo ts'a dge tshul khyung grags kyis //
T02TD2848E:188b-17: 'dul ba'i bstan pa snying por gnas pa'i sa //
T02TD2848E:188b-18: dpal ldan rgyan gong gtsug lag khang de ru //
T02TD2848E:188b-19: bder gshegs bstan la phan phyir bsgyur lags kyi //
T02TD2848E:188b-20: rnal 'byor spyod rnams nges par brtson par mdzod//
